00:01:31,528 --> 00:01:34,331
Satu kali, dua kali...

29
00:01:34,364 --> 00:01:37,034
Terjual seharga 41 juta.

30
00:01:37,067 --> 00:01:39,936
<i>Selamat, mobil itu milikmu, Pak.</i>

