bisa buat perbedaan besar.

57
00:02:49,906 --> 00:02:50,907
Jalan sana.

58
00:03:41,858 --> 00:03:42,859
Yang benar saja?

59
00:03:57,607 --> 00:03:58,608
Hah.

60
00:04:20,288 --> 00:04:21,488
Jangan berhenti.

61
00:04:24,376 --> 00:04:25,376
Jalan terus.

62
00:04:25,502 --> 00:04:26,502
Apa yang terjadi?

63
00:04:26,711 --> 00:04:27,831
Jalan terus!

64
00:04:35,929 --> 00:04:36,929
Lebih cepat!

65
00:04:40,316 --> 00:04:41,618
