68
00:05:25,829 --> 00:05:26,930
Hei, Sobat.

69
00:05:35,672 --> 00:05:36,752
Harusnya aku yang menyetir.

70
00:05:41,410 --> 00:05:42,812
Kau buat bensinnya banjir, Bung.

71
